ed="T" n="0801a17"/><persName key="A010792">釋如淨</persName>，不詳何許人也。甫參法位，當納<lb
ed="T" n="0801a18"/>戒<choice resp="sgsz"><sic>津</sic><corr>律</corr></choice>，明練毘尼<ptr type="glossary" target="#g900"/>，砥礪名節。時恒講勗，徒侶<lb
ed="T" n="0801a19"/>雲屯。辭筆偕長，博達儒典。先是<placeName key="PL000000042002">關中</placeName>行<persName key="A001269">智<lb
ed="T" n="0801a20"/>首<roleName>律師</roleName></persName>《四分律疏》<ptr target="#n941"/>，<placeName key="PL000000024082">魏郡</placeName><persName key="A000747">法礪<roleName>律師</roleName></persName>著《疏》<ptr target="#n903"/>別行。<lb
ed="T" n="0801a21"/>爾時<placeName key="PL000000042002">關輔</placeName><placeName key="PL000000001520">河北</placeName>，各競宗派，微似參、辰<ptr target="#n1211"/>。<date notBefore-iso="+0609-02-19" key="j19435421973336" notAfter-iso="+0690-09-16"><name>隋</name>末<name>唐</name><lb
ed="T" n="0801a22"/>初</date>，<persName key="A001519">道宣<roleName>律師</roleName></persName>以<persName key="A001269">首</persName>《大疏》為本，造《刪補律鈔》<ptr target="#n1290"/><lb
ed="T" n="0801a23"/>三卷，稍為會要<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g1198"/>，行事逗機<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1292"/>。<date from-iso="+0627-01-26" key="j19500921958296" to-iso="+0649-07-13"><name>貞觀</name></date>已來，<placeName key="PL000000042002">三輔</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000015039">江<lb
ed="T" n="0801a24"/>淮</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000035107">岷蜀</placeName>多傳唱之。次<persName key="A000294"><anchor xml:id="beg0801003"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>裝</sic><corr>奘</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0801003"/></persName>三藏弟子<persName key="A001899">懷素</persName>者，<lb
ed="T" n="0801a25"/>先習《鈔》宗，後委棄<persName key="A001519">宣</persName>、<persName key="A000747">礪</persName>之學，於<date notBefore-iso="+0670-03-30" key="j19658611967498" notAfter-iso="+0674-09-22"><name>咸亨</name>年中</date><ptr target="#n1446"/><lb
ed="T" n="0801a26"/>別述《開四分律記》<ptr target="#n902"/>，後號「新章」歟。至<persName key="A004379">代宗</persName><date notBefore-iso="+0766-12-22" key="j20011912005747" notAfter-iso="+0779-06-13"><name>大<lb
ed="T" n="0801a27"/>曆</name>中</date>，新章舊疏，互相長短。<date from-iso="+0778-02-06" key="j20052552005608" to-iso="+0779-01-25">十三年</date>，勅集三宗<ptr target="#n1520"/><lb
ed="T" n="0801a28"/>律匠，重定二家<ptr target="#n1550"/>隆殺<ptr type="glossary" target="#g555"/>，時<persName key="A010792">淨</persName>推為宗主<ptr target="#n1726"/>，語在<lb
ed="T" n="0801a29"/>〈圓照傳〉<ptr target="#n1727"/>。至<date from-iso="+0781-02-02" key="j20063472006701" to-iso="+0782-01-22"><name>建中</name>二年</date>，奏二疏並行，<persName key="A010792">淨</persName>之力也<ptr target="#n1725"/>。<pb ed="T" n="0801b" xml:id="T50.2061.0801b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0801b01"/>蓋以國相<persName key="A010790">元<roleName>公</roleName>載</persName>篤重<persName key="A001899">素<roleName>公</roleName></persName>，崇其律教，乃<lb
ed="T" n="0801b02"/>命<persName key="A010792">淨</persName>為新疏主作傳焉。</p>
